class ImageFolderDataset[source]

ImageFolderDataset(*args, **kwds) :: Dataset

Create Dataset instance from source using tfm

{% endraw %}

Required arguments :

  • source: Union[str, Path] - Source directory of the Images
  • tfm: ImageClassificationTransforms - Transformations to apply to the images

You can optinally pass in classes, which should be a Dict that contains a mapping of {class_name: interger_label}

Images should arranged in this way:

root/dog/xxx.png
root/dog/xxy.png
root/dog/xxz.png

root/cat/123.png
root/cat/nsdf3.png
root/cat/asd932_.png

{% include note.html content='loader is a function to load an image given its path.' %}

{% raw %} 
tfm = AugTransforms(p_cutout=0)
ds  = ImageFolderDataset(source=data_path, tfm=tfm, loader="cv2_loader")
dl  = DataLoader(ds, batch_size=8)
image, target = next(iter(dl))
plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
imshow_tensor(image, target, normalize=True)

INFO:__main__:Found 2000 files belonging to 2 classes.
{% endraw %}

Transformations can also be reloaded after instantiating the Dataset.

{% raw %}

ImageFolderDataset.reload_tfm[source]

ImageFolderDataset.reload_tfm(tfm:ImageClassificationTransforms)

reloads the transformations in the Dataset

{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
tfm = AugTransforms(p_cutout=1.0)
ds.reload_tfm(tfm)

dl  = DataLoader(ds, batch_size=8)
image, target = next(iter(dl))
plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
imshow_tensor(image, target, normalize=True)
